item.title: Cheat at live MD5 count
item.description: ##11:17 Friday 14 November 2014 JST## /u/artbn commented on the MD5 live count thing that he(?) spent 30 minutes searching for a string that would work for the next number, but came up with nothing. I offered to send him code to help find strings. He accepted so I pushed the code up to live md5 recursive cheater I’ve also got a slew of precomputed values which, as of this writing, I’ve pushed to an orphan branch (my first!
